<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=LDS_edition_of_the_Bible&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: External links"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<dl><dt>English-language edition</dt></dl>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://assets.churchofjesuschrist.org/17/72/17727a14764611edbd96eeeeac1e758ff584966c/bible_regular_simulated_black_unindexed.pdf">English-language LDS Church Bible</a>: complete text in PDF, including footnotes and chapter headings.</li>
