<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures?lang=eng">English-language Study Helps</a>: complete text in HTML of the topical index, bible dictionary, maps, and Joseph Smith Translation</li></ul>
<dl><dt>Spanish-language edition</dt></dl>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://media.ldscdn.org/pdf/lds-scriptures/holy-bible/holy-bible-34402-spa.pdf">Spanish-language LDS Church Bible</a>: complete text in PDF, including footnotes and chapter headings.</li>
