<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/nt/title-page?lang=spa">Spanish-language New Testament</a>: complete text in HTML, including footnotes and chapter headings</li></ul>
<dl><dt>Portuguese-language edition</dt></dl>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://media.ldscdn.org/pdf/lds-scriptures/holy-bible/holy-bible-83800-por.pdf">Portuguese-language LDS Church Bible</a>: complete text in PDF, including footnotes and chapter headings.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures?lang=por">Official webpage of Portuguese-language edition</a></li>
